            . I live in Colville-court, St. Pancras. On the 12th of October I was in <placeName id="t18341016-80-crimeloc449">Oxford-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18341016-80-crimeloc449" type="placeName" value="Oxford-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18341016-80-crimeloc449" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18341016-80-off447 t18341016-80-crimeloc449"></join> - I saw the prosecutor going along, and the prisoner and another lad - I saw the prisoner put his hand into the prosecutor's pocket, and he drew the purse out of his right hand coat pocket - the prisoner ran on the opposite side, towards me - as soon as he came to me, I laid hold of him - we had a bit of a scuffle - he threw the purse down - Evans picked it up, and we called the prosecutor.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18341016-80-person825">
